  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a rougelite card game that combines parkour-style with stock speculation. You can experience the journey from a stock trading novice to the most powerful king of stocks! More casual or more strategic? It's your choice!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Thrilling and Exciting Parkour Collection Experience!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/25a6ddfba21c23ff6aa68305fefdbadc.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/25a6ddfba21c23ff6aa68305fefdbadc.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/25a6ddfba21c23ff6aa68305fefdbadc.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Cash, items, stock trading, obstacles, fluctuating gates... nearly a hundred different objects appear along the track, with each encounter bringing surprises and rewards.<br>When enough rare metals are collected, you'll unlock a satisfying and delightful settlement experience, enjoying the thrill of money pouring into your pockets!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rich and Diverse Card Strategy!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/54ca87c04cf66e31868bbdf670d695b9.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/54ca87c04cf66e31868bbdf670d695b9.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/54ca87c04cf66e31868bbdf670d695b9.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Economic, growth, powerful decrement, and special effect cards... Over sixty different cards with unique functions allow you to build your own exclusive deck!<br>Card updates are ongoing~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unexpected and Exciting Events!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6c1cceea8dbc9bcffe0912376ec5e9f9.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6c1cceea8dbc9bcffe0912376ec5e9f9.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6c1cceea8dbc9bcffe0912376ec5e9f9.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You will face fifty sudden events that deeply impact stock prices. Pay close attention, as the secrets to wealth are hidden within them!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging Boss Levels with Varying Difficulty!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0ce0c522571e0007c184064532801b32.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0ce0c522571e0007c184064532801b32.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0ce0c522571e0007c184064532801b32.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Twelve main Greek gods correspond to twelve high-difficulty challenge levels. The gods are not selfless or void of desires; their inner darkness reflects the true nature of \"gods\"!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wide Variety of Game Items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/595dfff4aa6a59babc3daf10cb31cf56.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/595dfff4aa6a59babc3daf10cb31cf56.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/595dfff4aa6a59babc3daf10cb31cf56.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Wide-range collection, fast horizontal movement, price reversals... The fun item system makes parkour much more interesting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and enjoy it!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a rougelite card game that combines parkour-style with stock speculation. You can experience the journey from a stock trading novice to the most powerful king of stocks! More casual or more strategic? It's your choice!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Thrilling and Exciting Parkour Collection Experience!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/25a6ddfba21c23ff6aa68305fefdbadc.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/25a6ddfba21c23ff6aa68305fefdbadc.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/25a6ddfba21c23ff6aa68305fefdbadc.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Cash, items, stock trading, obstacles, fluctuating gates... nearly a hundred different objects appear along the track, with each encounter bringing surprises and rewards.<br>When enough rare metals are collected, you'll unlock a satisfying and delightful settlement experience, enjoying the thrill of money pouring into your pockets!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rich and Diverse Card Strategy!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/54ca87c04cf66e31868bbdf670d695b9.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/54ca87c04cf66e31868bbdf670d695b9.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/54ca87c04cf66e31868bbdf670d695b9.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Economic, growth, powerful decrement, and special effect cards... Over sixty different cards with unique functions allow you to build your own exclusive deck!<br>Card updates are ongoing~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unexpected and Exciting Events!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6c1cceea8dbc9bcffe0912376ec5e9f9.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6c1cceea8dbc9bcffe0912376ec5e9f9.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6c1cceea8dbc9bcffe0912376ec5e9f9.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You will face fifty sudden events that deeply impact stock prices. Pay close attention, as the secrets to wealth are hidden within them!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging Boss Levels with Varying Difficulty!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0ce0c522571e0007c184064532801b32.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0ce0c522571e0007c184064532801b32.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0ce0c522571e0007c184064532801b32.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Twelve main Greek gods correspond to twelve high-difficulty challenge levels. The gods are not selfless or void of desires; their inner darkness reflects the true nature of \"gods\"!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wide Variety of Game Items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/595dfff4aa6a59babc3daf10cb31cf56.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/595dfff4aa6a59babc3daf10cb31cf56.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/595dfff4aa6a59babc3daf10cb31cf56.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Wide-range collection, fast horizontal movement, price reversals... The fun item system makes parkour much more interesting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and enjoy it!</p>",
